{"tid":1653123,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《環時》：克魯茲訪港旨在破壞 應列禁入境名單","createTime":"2019-10-14T02:57:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T03:45:09.000Z","uid":28114,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6fcbc6eadc05f1084a224c8a6fce76e2b99f31fa","tid":1653123,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:57:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191014/large/1571013045_2a9f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191014%2Flarge%2F1571013045_2a9f.jpg&h=243d1d4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n克魯茲(路透社)<br />\n<br />\n美國國會即將復會，預計將會通過《香港人權與民主法案》，支持法案的參議員克魯茲（Ted Cruz）近日訪港，親身到現場觀察示威，並接受專訪，表明支持香港人爭取捍衞民主，並指美國支持港人符合利益。可是，中共喉舌《環球時報》卻批評，克魯茲訪港的目的是要「破壞香港穩定」，更稱如果美國國會通過法案，克魯茲及親屬應被列入禁止訪港的黑名單。<br />\n<br />\n這篇題為「美參議員赤膊上陣亂港，應受到制裁」的社論，直指克魯茲「雖然嘴上說他支持『非暴力』，但這一表態只是對他公開挺香港暴力示威的一種掩護。他來香港就是阻止理性在這座城市回升、煽動局勢增加熱度的，他是美國鼓動香港激進示威者『不要停下來』的活人喇叭」。<br />\n<br />\n社評又指出，立場「反華反共親台」的克魯茲，成為昨日香港「最突出的破壞性因素之一」，聲稱「他讓氣焰已經衰減的一些示威者產生一縷新的幻覺。克魯茲與香港激進示威者絕對是『一伙的』，他就差舉着一根鐵棍子加入暴徒的隊伍，直接打砸香港街頭的公共設施，或者對警察施暴了」。<br />\n<br />\n對於美國國會即將通過《香港人權與民主法案》，社評批評是「明目張膽地干涉香港事務」，更稱如果法案限制香港部份人進入美國，「以後克魯茲這樣的人也應被列入禁止訪港的黑名單，並且受到更多的制裁」。<br />\n<br />\n然而，克魯茲接受美國哥倫比亞廣播公司（CBS）專訪時，則表示他穿着黑色衣服在街上觀察，認為香港的示威仍然持續，而香港的示威活動亦極具啟發性。他認為香港市民企出來反對中共政權的打壓，美國支持香港人的行動，亦是十分符合美國的利益。<br />\n<br />\n《環球時報》/哥倫比亞廣播公司<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20191014/60151348?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191014%2F60151348%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=JMO6Z0a0EEbNsRtkVA0DAptjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=61e5b181\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191014%2F60151348%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=c29cffce\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20191014/60151348?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"fd8c4165abfde4edab8ec6abbe96ef187f19f8a5","tid":1653123,"uid":27432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:59:03.000Z","msg":"靚助攻~"},{"pid":"ae8490c30e93cf12bd949fe8d0eff28f4e18b914","tid":1653123,"uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:59:32.000Z","msg":"唔做正契弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecf0ddc0e4c0efe0a1a752278e66be9532ecac06","tid":1653123,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:59:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">twitter 缺人</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">大家幫幫手！養成每日retweet習慣！</span></span><br />\n大家可以用下twitter help 去每日領任務retweet！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=JMO6Z0a0EEbNsRtkVA0DAptjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=9b537e01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tKHAaEE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtKHAaEE.png&h=6b504c3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n只要輸入 /task2 就可以知道外國議員外媒名人出左咩重要tweet，大家去retweet啦！<